Details of how viewers voted in the just concluded Big Brother Naija 2019 have emerged. Mercy was declared winner of the show after scoring the highest vote. She won with a highest per cent of the vote cast. Mike trailed behind, while Seyi had the least vote. Here is a breakdown of how viewers voted: Mike:19.94% Mercy:41.77% Seyi:10.25% Frodd:16.46% Omashola:11.58%  Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.